title: Vienna Insurance expands business to northern Europe - Nasdaq.com
text: BERLIN, Sept 5 (Reuters) - Vienna Insurance Group  announced on Thursday it would intensify its activity in northern Europe, offering insurance to corporate customers through brokers.
The Austrian group will start operating in Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Finland, it said in a (graphic).
CEO Elisabeth Stadler said the company was still clearly committed to its strategy focused on central and eastern Europe.
